i\" /> 同埋老任根本don't give a shit<br />\n香港人把自己看得那麼高"},{"pid":"dec7175da187809c49e493e2d400a2ed975bfc4f","tid":483833,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 我連佢個台都未收到 <br />\n<br />\n有線收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱專登掃多次都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184a0bda7b025a6174e30569b366df9d91e02e40","tid":483833,"uid":1972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"之前game宣傳叫精靈pokemon 特登唔用中文 斬腳指"},{"pid":"bba10b143fe4e94fee38ae0408b814acd1951e20","tid":483833,"uid":1972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前game宣傳叫精靈pokemon 特登唔用中文 斬腳趾</blockquote>"},{"pid":"80f14935df52df96180b86641f2bbf4f9e10847c","tid":483833,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"本身奇妙個台已經冇咩好睇，夜晚成日都係泡菜支那劇<br />\n仲要咁冇骨氣買寶可夢返嚟播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296f3a9aa359d9e1872c3d8efd58de90308115ee","tid":483833,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 我連佢個台都未收到 <br />\n<br />\n有線收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱專登掃多次都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n官網check下有冇覆蓋<br />\n如果有應該都裝好晒"}]}